itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T00:13:37.000Z","msg":"本身撞鳩左對家<br />\n就肯定入一條 不小心<br />\n<br />\n如果當時仲著住拖鞋 <br />\n咁就有條件可以再升一級 入你危險駕駛<br />\n<br />\n拖鞋定義係有冇鞋爭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2RwGhsg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2RwGhsg.jpg&h=0841c0da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似呢隻咁 條鞋爭帶 向後<br />\n咁就唔算拖鞋"},{"pid":"6e280cb0182c7d589da57ac7eb6d784ea08c6fe6","tid":2006304,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T00:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71fab46d93e7fbf865d5f4319e7aa391f2d798f","tid":2006304,"uid":357234,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T00:21:56.000Z","msg":"諗起個朋友唔鐘意著鞋揸車<br />\n五隻肥肥地嘅腳趾踩油門幾得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08db6d2cf37d2981ace74bc0fda5d1e19f25a49c","tid":2006304,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T01:03:35.000Z","msg":"著高踭鞋又點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c4f07093ec8147fc524f11dce4f17ed11c1af74","tid":2006304,"uid":21871,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"caae196ebe73be8c3ceaeef9645e088ce07355f6","tid":2006304,"uid":60860,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T00:12:08.000Z","msg":"試過一次去沙灘貪方便<br />\n真係衰過唔著鞋揸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T02:40:06.000Z","msg":"唔著鞋先最爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b238a9d1618db47a622fae0c08a3220cb6bca3c3","tid":2006304,"uid":200247,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5efcf116ac5406327b25e3633f01b2f58ef438c1","tid":2006304,"uid":142116,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T20:19:37.000Z","msg":"試過著拖鞋揸 但無上高速<br />\n拖鞋輕 踩油/腳制要用多啲力"},"citedBy":0,"re